@startuml UC-CM-07: View Payslip

actor "Người dùng" as User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "PayrollController" as API
participant "PayrollService" as Svc
database "payroll_periods / payslips" as DB

User -> FE: Chọn "Phiếu lương"
FE -> API: GET /api/v1/payroll/my-payslips
API -> Svc: getMyPayslips(currentUser.id)
Svc -> DB: findPayslipsByUserId(userId)
DB --> Svc: List<Payslip>
Svc --> API: List<Payslip>
API --> FE: 200 List<Payslip>
FE --> User: Hiển thị DS kỳ lương

User -> FE: Chọn kỳ lương → Xem chi tiết
FE --> User: baseSalary, bonus, deduction,\nadvanceDeduct, finalNetSalary

opt Tải PDF
    User -> FE: Nhấn "Tải PDF"
    FE -> API: GET /api/v1/payroll/payslips/{id}/pdf
    API -> Svc: generatePayslipPdf(payslipId)
    Svc --> API: byte[] PDF
    API --> FE: 200 application/pdf
    FE --> User: Download file PDF
end

@enduml
